short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Clicking 'videos' on google search redirects the search to YouTube

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Remember the good old days when google search would have a 'YouTube' tab? This extension brings the YouTube tab back, allowing you to move search queries to youtube easily from google.
